race.comment: ACE'S CHANCE (5) boasts a strong record this journey with four wins and two minors from nine tries. Scored by 1.3 lengths last time (16.94) in a Invitation over 300m at this track. Expected to be in the finish. SOMNAMBULIST (8) was a narrow winner last time, jumping from this same box to score by a nose in a Invitation over 300m at this track. Should be in this for a long way. LIP TRICKS (2) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close second, 1.3 lengths from the winner ACE'S CHANCE (17.03) at this track. Winning chance. STORMY DAY (1) is worth consideration after filling a hole at this course and distance last start.
